return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.1','translation-revision-date'=>'2023-11-06 06:11:14+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','project-id-version'=>'Themes - Twenty Fourteen','language'=>'zh_TW','messages'=>['In 2014, our default theme lets you create a responsive magazine website with a sleek, modern design. Feature your favorite homepage content in either a grid or a slider. Use the three widget areas to customize your website, and change your content\'s layout with a full-width page template and a contributor page to show off your authors. Creating a magazine website with WordPress has never been easier.'=>'2014 年推出的預設佈景主題 Twenty Fourteen，讓大家可以輕鬆建立一個具備時尚現代設計的回應式雜誌風格網站。使用者可以將精選內容以格狀或輪播方式顯示於首頁，還可以使用 3 個小工具區域自訂網站，並將網站的版面配置變更為 Full Width Page 範本，以及透過 Contributor Page 範本展示網站的作者群。使用 WordPress 建立一個雜誌風格網站，從未如此簡單。','Twenty Fourteen'=>'Twenty Fourteen','GET IN TOUCH'=>'保持聯絡','Don’t hesitate to reach out.'=>'請隨時與我聯絡。','GOT A QUESTION?'=>'是否想提出問題？','Write title…'=>'撰寫標題...','Contact'=>'聯絡方式','Read More'=>'閱讀全文','Clouds'=>'雲霧環繞','Photo of a cloudy mountain'=>'雲霧環繞的山的照片','Streetscape'=>'街景','Photo of a streetscape'=>'街景的照片','Bridge'=>'橋樑','Photo of a bridge'=>'橋樑的照片','Sunset'=>'日落','Photo of a sunset'=>'日落的照片','Here are some photos from my all-time favorite destinations.'=>'我精選了在所有旅程中最愛的旅行地點的照片。','Traveling Nostalgia'=>'念念不忘的地點','Summary'=>'摘要','This year was devoted entirely to the western hemisphere. I went on a month-long road trip through the U.S.A. and Canada, and also visited Mexico, Brazil, and Colombia.'=>'這年完全聚焦在西半球，並在美國及加拿大進行了為期一個月的公路旅行，之後也造訪了墨西哥、巴西及哥倫比亞。',2016=>'2016 年','In 2012, I expanded my travels to Europe. I spent time in Poland, Germany, Italy, France, and Spain.'=>'在 2012 年，我將旅行地點擴展到歐洲，並在波蘭、德國、義大利、法國及西班牙度過一段時光。',2012=>'2012 年','My first year of traveling. I visited China, Thailand, Japan, and India.'=>'第一次出遊的年份，造訪了台灣、泰國、日本及印度。',2001=>'2001 年','List'=>'清單','I’ve traveled to over 60 countries, and have made many friends along the way. I created this